  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The sequel to Carnage Heart, a mecha action-strategy game from Artdink.\n\nDesign an unmanned mobile weapon overkill engine, direct the airframe designed by himself and lead the battle to victory.\n\nAddition of story part, numerous new aircraft, strengthening of graphics, improvement of operability and completely revamp the system of the previous work.\n\nThe curtain of dramatic SF simulation set on Jupiter's satellite rises!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "2098 AD.\nWorkers in the resource mining district, the Asteroid Belt, declared independence from the Martian nation and staged an armed uprising. OKE Delta Squadron rookie Mark Grant is dispatched to a battlefield illuminated by the faint light of the solarized Jupiter \"Zeus\". But on his way...",
